Package sg.edu.cs2103aug2015_w13_2j.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddHandler
    CommandHandler which handles adding a Task object to the master list of Task objects.
    CommandHandler
    Base abstract class inherited by all command handlers.
    DeleteHandler
    CommandHandler which handles deleting one or more Task objects from the master list of Task objects.
    EditHandler
    CommandHandler which handles editing the details of a Task object in the master list of Task objects.
    FilterHandler
    CommandHandler which handles filtering Task objects to obtain a subset of Task objects with specific properties.
    HelpHandler
    CommandHandler which handles showing the FunDUE Help Page to the user.
    LoadHandler
    CommandHandler which handles showing a file picker dialog to change the FunDUE Data File.
    MarkCompletedHandler
    Marks a Task indicated by the user as "Completed" or "Uncompleted".
    MarkImportantHandler
    Toggles a Task specified by the user as "Important" or "Unimportant".
    PopHandler
    Pops or removes a filter already specified by the user.
    RedoHandler
    Redoes a command previously undone using the "Undo" command by the user.
    SearchHandler
    CommandHandler which handles searching for Task objects containing one or more specified search terms.
    UndoHandler
    Undoes a command made by the user.
